snippet.title: 9 Mins Gameplay : Rise Of The Triad (No Commentary)
snippet.description:
Rise Of The Triad.
Campaign , Normal difficulty (I think).
No it's not speeded up (google it , this is the way you say it) I'm just using the redhead.

Yeah , graphics on max.

Subscribe for more videos.

What is RoTT?
Just watch the video.Then go on Steam and buy it.If you don't have Steam download it.If you don't have a PC build one.Blah blah blah either way you'll end up dead.Might as well play Rise Of The Triad.That pretty much sums it up.

Available on Steam : http://store.steampowered.com/app/217140/
